Website Feedback






Please use this form to report a problem with a University web page, ask questions related to our website, or send us your website-related comments. This form sends email to webmaster@sonoma.edu. Your feedback helps us improve our site's content and usability, so your time is appreciated.
If you have questions or comments about the University, please use the Comments form.
If you need assistance with a computing account or password, access to online systems (such as email and registration), contact the IT Helpdesk.
If you want information about applying to SSU, please visit the Admissions Contact page for further contact information.
